    "methodology": "Student loan data from SLC annual statistical reports. Enrollment figures from HESA Student Record via Jisc. Graduate outcomes from the DfE Longitudinal Education Outcomes (LEO) dataset, which links higher education records with HMRC tax data. Degree classifications from HESA aggregate data. Non-continuation rates from OfS registration data. All figures relate to UK higher education providers unless otherwise stated.",
    "knownIssues": [
      "COVID-19 affected 2020 and 2021 degree classifications \u2014 many universities adopted 'no detriment' policies that inflated grades",
      "The LEO earnings data has a 5-year lag \u2014 the latest figures show graduates from 2018/19 cohorts",
      "International student figures for 2024/25 are provisional and subject to revision",
      "Student loan repayment forecasts are highly sensitive to future earnings growth assumptions"
    ]
  }
